  "budgetFormula": {
    "charsPerLine": "floor(w / (fontSize * 0.52))",
    "maxLines": "max(1, floor(h / (fontSize * 1.25)))",
    "charCap": "charsPerLine * maxLines",
    "note": "Lock-the-box: generate to charCap, autofit font down to a floor, then shorten content — never grow the box. Fixed-by-role slots (title, eyebrow-label, metric-value, metric-label, delta, footer) are identical at every density tier; only body-type slots scale."
